responseText: NSLOCTEXT("", "DE873DD141A7445A075D72B214994D97", "Oh. Yes. I nearly--ahem--forgot. Here: take this note to an herbalist or a butcher. It\'ll pay to have what I need delivered here, but there\'s not enough for both plants and herbs. I leave the choice to you.")
